summary: Makes access to the Arch-Mage\'s Quarters easier.
descriptionHtml:
A very simple mod I made to see how doors and locking works with the Creation Kit, which adds a trapdoor leading to the Arch-Mage\'s Quarters near the College of Winterhold fast travel location.

Requires the keys to the room so you don\'t simply get access to free housing.

Will probably conflict with other mods that modifies the room, such as Malevolent Hospitality\'s [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=8661]ArchMageQuartersMinimalMod[/url].

[update]
Confirmed to work with mgbeach\'s [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=9053]Drakespire Archmage Office[/url]!
author: Pizzaman
